{"text_id":34727,"tokens":["Mandatory"," community"," service"," for"," students"," has"," been"," a"," topic"," of"," debate"," for"," years","."," On"," one"," hand",","," proponents"," argue"," that"," it"," instill","s"," a"," sense"," of"," civic"," responsibility"," and"," contributes"," to"," personal"," growth","."," On"," the"," other"," hand",","," opponents"," argue"," that"," it"," places"," an"," unfair"," burden"," on"," students"," and"," may"," lead"," to"," a"," lack"," of"," genuine"," motivation","."," Both"," perspectives"," have"," valid"," points",","," but"," after"," careful"," consideration",","," I"," firmly"," believe"," that"," introducing"," mandatory"," community"," service"," for"," students"," is"," a"," valuable"," initiative",".","\n","One"," of"," the"," major"," advantages"," of"," mandatory"," community"," service"," is"," that"," it"," helps"," students"," develop"," a"," sense"," of"," social"," responsibility","."," By"," actively"," participating"," in"," their"," community",","," students"," learn"," the"," importance"," of"," giving"," back"," and"," become"," more"," empathetic"," towards"," others","."," For"," instance",","," a"," study"," conducted"," by"," the"," Corporation"," for"," National"," and"," Community"," Service"," found"," that"," high"," school"," students"," who"," engaged"," in"," community"," service"," were"," more"," likely"," to"," develop"," a"," lifelong"," commitment"," to"," volunteer","ism",".","\n","Furthermore",","," mandatory"," community"," service"," can"," also"," enhance"," a"," student","'","s"," personal"," growth","."," Through"," these"," experiences",","," students"," are"," exposed"," to"," diverse"," environments"," and"," cultures",","," teaching"," them"," important"," life"," skills"," such"," as"," effective"," communication"," and"," teamwork","."," For"," instance",","," a"," survey"," conducted"," by"," the"," National"," Association"," for"," College"," Admission"," Counseling"," revealed"," that"," colleges"," and"," universities"," value"," community"," service"," experience"," because"," it"," helps"," students"," develop"," important"," skills"," and"," characteristics"," that"," can"," contribute"," to"," success"," in"," higher"," education",".","\n","However",","," opponents"," argue"," that"," mandatory"," community"," service"," can"," create"," time"," constraints"," and"," interfere"," with"," a"," student","'","s"," personal"," respon","sibilities","."," Students"," have"," a"," heavy"," workload"," with"," academic"," studies"," and"," extracurricular"," activities",","," and"," adding"," community"," service"," obligations"," can"," be"," overwhelming","."," Additionally",","," students"," may"," have"," other"," personal"," respon","sibilities",","," such"," as"," part","-","time"," jobs"," or"," caring"," for"," family"," members",","," that"," make"," it"," difficult"," to"," devote"," time"," to"," community"," service","."," Allowing"," flexibility"," in"," the"," hours"," and"," introducing"," options"," for"," virtual"," volunteering"," could"," address"," these"," concerns",".","\n","Some"," opponents"," also"," argue"," that"," mandatory"," community"," service"," may"," lead"," to"," a"," lack"," of"," genuine"," motivation","."," They"," argue"," that"," forcing"," students"," to"," participate"," takes"," away"," from"," the"," intrinsic"," desire"," to"," volunteer"," and"," may"," result"," in"," superficial"," or"," ins","incere"," efforts","."," It"," is"," important"," to"," address"," this"," concern"," and"," ensure"," that"," students"," understand"," the"," value"," of"," their"," contributions","."," By"," providing"," opportunities"," for"," meaningful"," engagement"," and"," reflecting"," on"," the"," impact"," of"," their"," actions",","," students"," can"," develop"," a"," genuine"," passion"," for"," serving"," their"," community",".","\n","In"," conclusion",","," mandatory"," community"," service"," for"," students"," is"," a"," valuable"," initiative"," that"," contributes"," to"," their"," personal"," growth"," and"," social"," responsibility","."," While"," there"," may"," be"," concerns"," regarding"," time"," constraints"," and"," motivation",","," these"," issues"," can"," be"," addressed"," through"," flexibility"," in"," hours"," and"," fostering"," meaningful"," engagement","."," By"," implementing"," mandatory"," community"," service",","," we"," can"," foster"," a"," generation"," of"," empathetic"," and"," responsible"," citizens"," who"," are"," committed"," to"," making"," a"," positive"," impact"," on"," their"," communities","."],"sub_source":"outfox","model":"gpt-3.5-turbo","label":1}